reviewText: There's nothing like good ole southern gospel music the music that I grew up with, that can make one cry laugh praise get in the spirit. Praise ye the Lord.
Love listening  and  watching  this  every Sabbath  .
Not good color and the DVD freezes all throughout it. Has great sound and picture is good. Other than the bad color and DVD skipping at times it was a good price compared to buying from Gaithers.com.
The tape was in great shape ,and very  quick delivery,and we enjoyed the tape very much and hope to order some mor later on
THis is another very well done Gaither Gospel Series video.  I loved it and would highly recommend it to any gospel music or Bill Gaither music lover.
